t%E1%BA%ADn-l%E1%BB%AF-ho%C3%A0i/poem-i7RG2ImFGP7zLMtOeRV8mg">Đô hạ vô ưu quán tiểu lâu xuân tận lữ hoài - 都下無懮館小樓春盡旅懷</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-V%E1%BA%A1n-L%C3%BD/author-JSRpfYAHfq-c4bVKwnYGVg">Dương Vạn Lý</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tu%E1%BB%87-Trung-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-s%C4%A9/Giang-h%E1%BB%93-t%E1%BB%B1-th%C3%ADch-II/poem-WH5BmlzO8Fh2vdPmFFKJcQ">Giang hồ tự thích (II) - 江湖自適</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tu%E1%BB%87-Trung-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-s%C4%A9/author-vnduJD_TYrIrUDl9fyOqRw">Tuệ Trung thượng sĩ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ki%E1%BB%81u-Tri-Chi/Kh%C3%AD-thi%E1%BA%BFp-thi%C3%AAn/poem-tK2KkOKnqkFHXzeyJegLzQ">Khí thiếp thiên - 棄妾篇</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ki%E1%BB%81u-Tri-Chi/author-Lsg5FCAGLlUg9HfTUhcnjw">Kiều Tri Chi</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/T%E1%BB%91ng-B%C3%B9i-th%E1%BA%ADp-b%C3%A1t-%C4%91%E1%BB%93-nam-quy-Tung-S%C6%A1n-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-K-_IlrL65DapS40ui2kjSA">Tống Bùi thập bát đồ nam quy Tung Sơn kỳ 2 - 送裴十八圖南歸嵩山其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-Nh%E1%BA%A1c/T%E1%BB%91ng-L%C3%BD-Tr%E1%BB%8Dng-T%C3%A2n-Ti%C3%AAu-Ph%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Nhai-xu%E1%BA%A5t-s%E1%BB%A9-An-Nam/poem-S3JvrJvDMDAE10CHsS69wQ">Tống Lý Trọng Tân, Tiêu Phương Nhai xuất sứ An Nam - 送李仲賓蕭方崖出使安南其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-Nh%E1%BA%A1c/author-qp8R9qKD4FVDvlYuA9e5wA">Lưu Nhạc</a>)<br></div>	</div>
